    "body": "Problem: The logic for generating backup file names is duplicated in `buf_write_make_backup` and difficult to reuse.\r\n\r\nSolution: Extract name generation logic into `buf_get_backup_name`.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/36262#discussion_r2558733977\r\n            ",
